CustomField.description: Check this box to enable TimeTrade Salesforce Calendar Sync. These features allows non-TimeTrade Events to be pushed to TimeTrade. Do not enable this feature if you have an existing calendar integration configured within TimeTrade.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Check this box to enable TimeTrade Salesforce Calendar Sync. These features allows non-TimeTrade Events to be pushed to TimeTrade. Do not enable this feature if you have an existing calendar integration configured within TimeTrade.
CustomField.label: Enable Salesforce Calendar Sync
